title: Чикули
overview: "Chikuli" - a new reality experiment that breaks stereotypes. Pretty girls and chiculi must spiritually enrich each other in the struggle for a cash prize. Fashionistas master molecular chemistry, coding and Silver Age poets, while geeks learn the art of blogging, progressives and how to fashionably combine socks with sandals.The hosts are blogger Vika Chuma and actor Mikael Aramyan.
